<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Restapi</title>

  <meta name="description" content="Rest Api adalah Restfull API yang dibuat dengan Node.js">
  <meta name="author" content="Faris">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;600&family=Inter:wght@300;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
* {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    }
    
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* Navbar */
    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 15px 50px;
      z-index: 1000;
    }
    
     .about, .services {
    padding: 50px;
    text-align: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    margin: 50px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .about h2, .services h2 {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, cyan, violet);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .about p, .services p {
    font-size: 18px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .service-list {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .service-item {
    width: 300px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .service-item i {
    font-size: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: cyan;
  }

  .service-item h3 {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
    
    .nav_logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: white;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    
    .nav_logo:hover {
      color: cyan;
    }

    .menu_items {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .menu_items a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: white;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    
    .menu_items a:hover {
      color: cyan;
    }

    #menu_toggle {
      display: none;
      font-size: 24px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      padding: 50px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, cyan, violet);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    
    .hero p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
    
    .btn {
      padding: 12px 25px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 50px;
      border: 1px solid white;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: white;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background: white;
      color: black;
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    /* Music Player */
    .music-player {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .music-player i {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .music-player i:hover {
      color: cyan;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: white;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header {
        padding: 15px 30px;
      }

      .menu_items {
        display: none;
        flex-direction: column;
        position: absolute;
        top: 60px;
        right: 30px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 10px;
      }

      .menu_open .menu_items {
        display: flex;
      }

      #menu_toggle {
        display: block;
      }
    }
</style>
      
</head>
<body>

  <header>
   <h2>Faris</h2>
    <ul class="menu_items">
      <a href="index.html">Home</a>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#service">Service</a>
      <a href="/api">Docs</a>
    </ul>
    <i id="menu_toggle" class="fa fa-bars"></i>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h2>Butuh Rest Api Gratis?</h2>
    <p>Kami menyediakan Restful Api Gratis untuk berbagai kebutuhan Anda.</p>
    <a href="/api"><button class="btn">Get Started</button></a>
  </section>
  
<section id="about" class="about">
  <h2>Tentang Kami</h2>
  <p>Kami menyediakan Restful API gratis yang dapat digunakan untuk berbagai kebutuhan developer.</p>
  <p>API kami dirancang dengan performa tinggi, mudah digunakan, dan memiliki dokumentasi lengkap.</p>
</section>

<section id="service" class="services">
  <h2>Layanan Kami</h2>
  <div class="service-list">
    <div class="service-item">
      <i class="fa fa-database"></i>
      <h3>Data API</h3>
      <p>API dengan berbagai data yang dapat digunakan untuk aplikasi Anda.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-item">
      <i class="fa fa-bolt"></i>
      <h3>Performa Tinggi</h3>
      <p>Server kami dioptimalkan untuk kecepatan dan stabilitas.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-item">
      <i class="fa fa-lock"></i>
      <h3>Keamanan Terjamin</h3>
      <p>Keamanan data menjadi prioritas utama dalam setiap layanan API kami.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  <div class="music-player">
    <i id="playPause" class="fa fa-play"></i>
    <audio id="backgroundMusic" loop>
      <source src="https://www.bensound.com/bensound-music/bensound-hey.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
      Your browser does not support the audio element.
    </audio>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>Â© 2024 Faris API. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    // Navbar Toggle
    document.querySelector("#menu_toggle").addEventListener("click", () => {
      document.querySelector("header").classList.toggle("menu_open");
    });

    // Music Player
    const music = document.getElementById("backgroundMusic");
    const playPause = document.getElementById("playPause");

    playPause.addEventListener("click", () => {
      if (music.paused) {
        music.play();
        playPause.classList.replace("fa-play", "fa-pause");
      } else {
        music.pause();
        playPause.classList.replace("fa-pause", "fa-play");
      }
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>
